HEADWORD: Sakti
<hw>Sak"ti</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.]</ety>
<fld>(Hind. Myth.)</fld> <def>The divine energy, personified as the wife
of a deity (Brahma, Vishnu, Siva, etc.); the female principle.</def>⟦br⟧
